    {
      "item_id": "e361c27c27:144",
      "text": "New bucket indicator（新 Bucket 指示器）",
      "ascii_letters": 24,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e361c27c27:145",
      "text": "允许你编辑 recent bucket marker 的颜色。参见",
      "ascii_letters": 18,
      "cjk_chars": 10
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e361c27c27:146",
      "text": "Recent Bucket Markers",
      "ascii_letters": 19,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e361c27c27:149",
      "text": "Focus Incoming Render（聚焦传入渲染）",
      "ascii_letters": 19,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e361c27c27:151",
      "text": "Display Mapping（显示映射）",
      "ascii_letters": 14,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e361c27c27:152",
      "text": "设置从 remap 菜单选择 Automatic view mapping 时要使用的 view mapping，并按不同 bit depths（8-bit、16-bit、Float）以及图像来自传入渲染还是磁盘分别设置。",
      "ascii_letters": 56,
      "cjk_chars": 34
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e361c27c27:153",
      "text": "Shortcuts（快捷键）",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 3
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e361c27c27:155",
      "text": "Special \"it\" Features（特殊 \"it\" 功能）",
      "ascii_letters": 19,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e361c27c27:156",
      "text": "AI Denoise（AI 降噪）",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 2
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e361c27c27:158",
      "text": "Nvidia's AI Denoising",
      "ascii_letters": 18,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e361c27c27:163",
      "text": "Denoising options 需要统计独立的像素，这意味着你要么手动为像素提供 rendering option \"Importance Sample Filtering\"，要么在相应桥接产品中选择 Denoise 选项，由其强制对图像使用 Importance Sample Filter。如果未启用此项，使用 Optix Denoiser 时将看不到变化。",
      "ascii_letters": 98,
      "cjk_chars": 62
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e361c27c27:165",
      "text": "Snapshot（快照）",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 2
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e361c27c27:169",
      "text": "Custom View",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e361c27c27:171",
      "text": "Custom View",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e361c27c27:174",
      "text": "Recent Bucket Markers（最近 Bucket 标记）",
      "ascii_letters": 25,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e361c27c27:176",
      "text": "Background（背景）",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 2
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e361c27c27:178",
      "text": "Background",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e361c27c27:182",
      "text": "Image->Toggle Background",
      "ascii_letters": 21,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e361c27c27:184",
      "text": "Working With Background Images（使用背景图像）。",
      "ascii_letters": 27,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e361c27c27:185",
      "text": "Remapping（重映射）",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 3
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e361c27c27:188",
      "text": "OpenColorIO",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e361c27c27:189",
      "text": "system 对 output images 进行 view mapping，以适配你选择的 workflow。你的 view mapping defaults 可以分别为渲染到 \"it\" 作为 frame buffer 的图像（无论 bit depth）或 imported images 设置（如有需要，也可针对不同类型使用不同 mapping）。",
      "ascii_letters": 98,
      "cjk_chars": 46
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e361c27c27:192",
      "text": "Burn Mapping On Save",
      "ascii_letters": 17,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e361c27c27:194",
      "text": "通过 RenderMan rendering 得到的图像默认位于 linear space，除非对 output 应用了 exposure（这可以在 RfM 中通过 RenderMan controls 的 Output Settings 选项卡完成）。",
      "ascii_letters": 77,
      "cjk_chars": 30
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e361c27c27:195",
      "text": "如果确实对 output 应用了 exposure，请确保对 rendered images 的 default image mapping 进行适当调整。",
      "ascii_letters": 47,
      "cjk_chars": 19
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e361c27c27:196",
      "text": "OpenColorIO setup 可以通过 it.ini 更改；不过一如既往，我们强烈建议在 site-specific surrogate ini 文件中进行更改，并通过 RMS_SCRIPT_PATHS 引用。若设置了环境变量 OCIO，\"it\" 也会使用它来查找 OpenColorIO config 文件。",
      "ascii_letters": 82,
      "cjk_chars": 49
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e361c27c27:198",
      "text": "Sequences（序列）",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 2
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e361c27c27:201",
